{
  "page": "Windproud",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Windproud_(ACOK_Comic).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6a/Windproud_%28ACOK_Comic%29.jpg/300px-Windproud_%28ACOK_Comic%29.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6a/Windproud_%28ACOK_Comic%29.jpg/450px-Windproud_%28ACOK_Comic%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/6/6a/Windproud_%28ACOK_Comic%29.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Windproud_(ACOK_Comic).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><i>Windproud</i> by Mel Rubi</div></div></div>\n<p><i><b>Windproud</b></i> was a two-masted galley belonging to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a>. It had a hundred oarsmen and sailors.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Windproud&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Baratheon\" title=\"Steffon Baratheon\">Steffon Baratheon</a> and his wife, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Cassana_Estermont\" title=\"Cassana Estermont\">Cassana Estermont</a>, took <i>Windproud</i> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> to search for a wife for Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a>, the son of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>. On their return trip, however, the ship broke up during a storm in <a href=\"/index.php/Shipbreaker_Bay\" title=\"Shipbreaker Bay\">Shipbreaker Bay</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> watched the destruction of their parents' ship from <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>. All lives were lost with the exception of <a href=\"/index.php/Patchface\" title=\"Patchface\">Patchface</a>, who washed up on shore three days later, half-mad.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Windproud&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I stopped believing in gods the day I saw the <i>Windproud</i> break up across <a href=\"/index.php/Shipbreaker_Bay\" title=\"Shipbreaker Bay\">the bay</a>. Any <a href=\"/index.php/Gods\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gods\">gods</a> so monstrous as to drown <a href=\"/index.php/Cassana_Estermont\" title=\"Cassana Estermont\">my mother</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Baratheon\" title=\"Steffon Baratheon\">father</a> would never have <i>my</i> worship, I vowed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Windproud&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Prologue\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Prologue\">Prologue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405030122\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.037 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.137 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 165/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8707/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1516/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 474/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1121/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50